Artist.....: Aphex Twin
Aliases....: Aphex Twin, Mike & Rich, AFX, Plygon Window, 
............ Caustic Window and Universal Indicator
Album......: Aphex Cholexion
Type.......: Self collected "Best of" album
Year.......: 2006
Genre......: Electronic
Quality....: Various 128+


This is a selfmade "best of" collection for those who want get familiar with 
one of the geniuses of electronic music - Richard D. James. All tracks are hand picked, rated 3-5 stars (MediaMonkey 3) and very listenable even for gentle ears.>)

Richard David James, is an electronic music artist, credited
with pushing forward the genres of techno, ambient, 
acid, and drum and bass.
